item.title: CVE-2021-32993|2024-09-17T03:52:56.730Z -- philips -- intellibridge%20ec%2040%20hub
item.description: IntelliBridge EC 40 and 60 Hub (C.00.04 and prior) contains hard-coded credentials, such as a password or a cryptographic key, which it uses for its own inbound authentication, outbound communication to external components, or encryption of internal data.
